          "date": "2018-08-19 18:30:13.000000000",
          "tz": 180
        },
        "subject": "LU-11250 migrate: Wrong transaction order in mdd_migrate_entries",
        "message": "LU-11250 migrate: Wrong transaction order in mdd_migrate_entries\n\nTransaction should start prior to mdd_write_lock otherwise\nit leads to a deadlock.\n\nThread 1:                 Thread 2:\n__schedule                __schedule\nschedule                   schedule\nwait_transaction_locked    rwsem_down_write_failed\nadd_transaction_credits    call_rwsem_down_write_failed\nstart_this_handle          down_write\njbd2__journal_start        osd_write_lock\n__ldiskfs_journal_start_sb lod_write_lock\nosd_trans_start            mdd_write_lock\ntop_trans_start            mdd_xattr_set\nlod_trans_start            mdt_reint_setxattr\nmdd_trans_start            mdt_reint_rec\nmdd_migrate_entries        mdt_reint_internal\nmdd_migrate                mdt_reint\nmdt_reint_migrate_internal tgt_request_handle\n\nChange-Id: I594ea904d2cd74b7568997da585c95c0e46e89d2\nCray-bug-id: LUS-6270\nSigned-off-by: Andriy Skulysh <c17819@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Alexander Boyko <c17825@cray.com>\nReviewed-by: Andrew Perepechko <c17827@cray.com>\nTested-by: Elena Gryaznova <c17455@cray.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
